data.description:
Updated split level home!  
This home offers 5 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms and 2 living spaces! Upstairs you will find; living room, kitchen, formal dining, full bath and 2 bedrooms! Updated kitchen with new black stainless steel appliances! Down stairs; is a second living space, true primary suite and 2 more bedrooms. The 5th bedroom can be used as an office space, home gym or bedroom with it's own exterior entrance! Detached 2 car garage with plenty of parking front and back. Short walk to hiking and biking trails.  Come see it for yourself !! Seller is offering $5,000 in seller concessions for closing costs, rate buy downs, additional improvements of buyers choice.
